---

<Layout
	title="Creattia | La plataforma N°1 para generar imágenes que venden"
	description="Convertí tu web y tus productos en imágenes publicitarias listas para vender. Sin diseñar ni escribir prompts."
	ogTitle="Creattia | Imágenes publicitarias para tu negocio"
	ogDescription="Elegí una idea, sumá tu producto y generá imágenes listas para publicar."
>
	<link rel="preload" href="https://tryholo.ai/fonts/Satoshi-Variable.woff2" as="font" crossorigin="anonymous" type="font/woff2" slot="head" />
	<link rel="preload" href="https://tryholo.ai/fonts/Satoshi-VariableItalic.woff2" as="font" crossorigin="anonymous" type="font/woff2" slot="head" />
	<link rel="preload" href="https://tryholo.ai/fonts/Wonderkids-Regular.ttf" as="font" crossorigin="anonymous" type="font/ttf" slot="head" />

	<!-- Header de Navegación -->
	<header class="floating-header" aria-label="Navegación principal">
		<a class="logo-bubble" href="#inicio" aria-label="Creattia, volver al inicio">
			<img src="/images/creattia/moki-mascot.webp" alt="Creattia Logo" width="1254" height="1254" decoding="async"/>
		</a>
		<nav class="nav-links">
			<a href="#como-funciona">Cómo funciona</a>
			<a href="#biblioteca">Biblioteca</a>
			<a href="#precios">Precios</a>
			<a href="/app/">Ingresar</a>
		</nav>
		<div class="header-actions">
			<a class="outline-cta" href="/app/">Empezar gratis <span>→</span></a>
			<a class="header-cta-mobile" href="/app/">Empezar gratis</a>
			<button class="mobile-menu-toggle" aria-label="Abrir menú" id="mobile-toggle">
				<span></span><span></span><span></span>
			</button>
		</div>
	</header>

	<!-- Menú móvil colapsable -->
	<div class="mobile-nav-overlay" id="mobile-overlay">
		<nav class="mobile-nav">
			<a href="#como-funciona" class="mobile-nav-link">Cómo funciona</a>
			<a href="#biblioteca" class="mobile-nav-link">Biblioteca</a>
			<a href="#precios" class="mobile-nav-link">Precios</a>
			<a href="/app/" class="mobile-nav-link">Ingresar</a>
			<a class="mobile-cta" href="/app/">Empezar gratis</a>
		</nav>
	</div>

	<main class="landing-content">
		<!-- Hero Section -->
		<section class="hero-section" id="inicio">
			<div class="hero-wrapper">
				<div class="hero-content-block">
					<div class="hero-badge-container">
						<div class="hero-badge">
							<span class="hero-badge-text">IA PARA MARKETING</span>
						</div>
					</div>
					<h1 class="hero-title">Los mejores creativos<br/>para tu negocio, con IA.</h1>
					<p class="hero-subtitle">Lanzá 10x más contenido, 75% más rápido. Creattia convierte tu web y tus productos en anuncios de alto rendimiento listos para publicar.</p>
					<div class="hero-actions">
						<a class="gradient-cta" href="/app/">
							<span>Empezar gratis</span>
							<svg class="cta-arrow" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.25"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"></path></svg>
						</a>
					</div>
					</div>
				<!-- Hero Video Container matching TryHolo look -->
				<div class="hero-video-container">
					<div class="video-border-effect"></div>
					<video autoplay muted loop playsinline preload="metadata" aria-label="Demostración de Creattia">
						<source src="/videos/creattia-hero-4x3.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
					</video>
				</div>

				<div class="hero-rating-wrapper">
					<div class="rating-stars">
						<div class="avatars-group">
							<img class="rating-avatar-img" src="https://tryholo.ai/rootPage/assets/SocialProof/footer-1.webp" alt="User 1" decoding="async" loading="lazy"/>
							<img class="rating-avatar-img" src="https://tryholo.ai/rootPage/assets/SocialProof/footer-2.webp" alt="User 2" decoding="async" loading="lazy"/>
							<img class="rating-avatar-img" src="https://tryholo.ai/rootPage/assets/SocialProof/footer-3.webp" alt="User 3" decoding="async" loading="lazy"/>
							<img class="rating-avatar-img" src="https://tryholo.ai/rootPage/assets/SocialProof/footer-4.webp" alt="User 4" decoding="async" loading="lazy"/>
						</div>
						<span class="rating-text"><strong>4.9</strong>/5 de más de <strong>4268</strong> clientes</span>
						<img class="rating-star-icon" src="https://tryholo.ai/rootPage/assets/SocialProof/startIcon.avif" alt="Star" decoding="async" loading="lazy"/>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Showcase Section (TryHolo Clone) -->
		<section class="showcase-section" id="biblioteca">
			<div class="showcase-container">
				<div class="showcase-header-wrapper">
					<h2 class="banner-heading">Probablemente ya viste nuestro trabajo.<br/>Solo que no sabías que era IA.</h2>
				</div>

				<div class="showcase-marquee" aria-label="Ejemplos de la biblioteca de Creattia">
					<div class="showcase-track">
						{showcase.map((item) => (
							<div class="showcase-card">
								<img src={item.src} alt={`Ejemplo de ${item.label}`} decoding="async" loading="lazy"/>
							</div>
						))}
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="showcase-footer-nav">
					<div class="carousel-nav-arrows">
						<button class="arrow-nav-btn prev-btn" aria-label="Anterior">
							<svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.25"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.5 19.5 3 12m0 0 7.5-7.5M3 12h18"/></svg>
						</button>
						<button class="arrow-nav-btn next-btn" aria-label="Siguiente">
							<svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.25"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/></svg>
						</button>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Manifesto Section with Inline Animating Videos (TryHolo Clone) -->
		<section class="manifesto-section">
			<div class="manifesto-container">
				<p class="manifesto-line">
					En Creattia estamos revolucionando cómo los creadores producen
					<span class="inline-video-wrapper">
						<video autoplay loop muted playsinline preload="metadata">
							<source src="https://tryholo.ai/rootPage/assets/integrationText/Bulb.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
						</video>
					</span>
					contenido.
				</p>
				<p class="manifesto-line">
					Usando los últimos modelos de IA capturamos
					<span class="inline-video-wrapper">
						<video autoplay loop muted playsinline preload="metadata">
							<source src="https://tryholo.ai/rootPage/assets/integrationText/brain.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
						</video>
					</span>
					la esencia de tu marca para entregar creativos de nivel de agencia en todas las
					<span class="inline-video-wrapper">
						<video autoplay loop muted playsinline preload="metadata">
							<source src="https://tryholo.ai/rootPage/assets/integrationText/socials.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
						</video>
					</span>
					plataformas.
				</p>
				<p class="manifesto-line">
					Para que puedas hacer el trabajo de un equipo completo
					<span class="inline-video-wrapper">
						<video autoplay loop muted playsinline preload="metadata">
							<source src="https://tryholo.ai/rootPage/assets/integrationText/team.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
						</video>
					</span>
					sin contratar uno.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Product Video Walkthrough Section (TryHolo Clone) -->
		<section class="walkthrough-video-section">
			<div class="walkthrough-video-wrapper">
				<div class="walkthrough-video-container">
					<video autoplay muted loop playsinline preload="metadata">
						<source src="https://czocbnyoenjbpxmcqobn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/creattia-media/walkthrough.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
					</video>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- How It Works Section (TryHolo Vertical Clone) -->
		<section class="how-it-works" id="como-funciona">
			<div class="section-header">
				<span class="section-tag font-bold">CÓMO FUNCIONA</span>
				<h2>De tu web a una imagen lista para vender.</h2>
			</div>
			
			<div class="steps-vertical-container">
				{steps.map((step, idx) => (
					<div class="step-vertical-row">
						<!-- Left indicator column -->
						<div class="step-left-line-col">
							<span class="step-vertical-number">{step.number}</span>
							{idx < steps.length - 1 && (
								<div class="step-vertical-line" style={`background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, ${idx === 0 ? '#3e86c6, #a666aa' : idx === 1 ? '#a666aa, #ec4492' : '#ee4454, #f05427'})`}></div>
							)}
						</div>
						
						<!-- Content and Demo columns -->
						<div class="step-vertical-content-wrapper">
							<div class="step-vertical-text">
								<h3>{step.title}</h3>
								<p>{step.copy}</p>
							</div>
							
							{step.kind !== 'publish' && (
								<div class="step-vertical-demo-box">
									{step.kind === 'url' && (
										<video autoplay loop muted playsinline class="step-video-demo">
											<source src="https://tryholo.ai/rootPage/assets/howItWorks/inputUrl.webm" type="video/webm" />
										</video>
									)}
									{step.kind === 'ideas' && (
										<video autoplay loop muted playsinline class="step-video-demo">
											<source src="https://tryholo.ai/rootPage/assets/howItWorks/SwipeIdeas.webm" type="video/webm" />
										</video>
									)}
									{step.kind === 'edit' && (
										<video autoplay loop muted playsinline class="step-video-demo">
											<source src="https://tryholo.ai/rootPage/assets/howItWorks/Edit.webm" type="video/webm" />
										</video>
									)}
								</div>
							)}
						</div>
					</div>
				))}
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- The All-in-One Marketing Tool Section (TryHolo 3D Cylinder Clone) -->
		<section class="all-in-one-section">
			<div class="section-header max-w-[800px] margin-auto">
				<span class="section-tag">LA HERRAMIENTA TODO EN UNO</span>
				<h2>La herramienta de marketing todo en uno.</h2>
				<p class="section-desc">Olvidate de las herramientas complejas, plantillas y pestañas. Creattia es la IA para tu marketing, diseñada para escalar tu negocio en piloto automático.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="cylinder-carousel-container">
				<div class="carousel-cylinder">
					{cylinderImages.map((src, idx) => {
						const angle = idx * 30; // 12 cards * 30deg = 360deg
						return (
							<div 
								class="cylinder-card" 
								style={`transform: rotateY(${angle}deg) translateZ(var(--carousel-radius));`}
							>
								<img src={src} alt={`Ejemplo creativo ${idx + 1}`} decoding="async" loading="lazy"/>
							</div>
						);
					})}
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Brand DNA Section -->
		<section class="brand-dna-section">
			<div class="section-header max-w-[800px] margin-auto">
				<span class="section-tag">IMPULSADO POR</span>
				<h2>El ADN de tu marca.</h2>
				<p class="section-desc">Creattia aprende lo que hace reconocible a tu negocio y lo reutiliza automáticamente cada vez que creás.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="dna-grid">
				<article class="dna-card style-card">
					<h3>Captura tu Estilo</h3>
					<p>Colores, tono, composición y forma de presentar tus productos.</p>
					<div class="color-dots-simulate">
						<span style="background: #3e86c6"></span>
						<span style="background: #a666aa"></span>
						<span style="background: #ec4492"></span>
						<span style="background: #ee4454"></span>
						<span style="background: #f05427"></span>
					</div>
				</article>

				<article class="dna-card triggers-card">
					<h3>Aprende Disparadores</h3>
					<p>Beneficios, urgencia, prueba social y argumentos comerciales de tu marca.</p>
					<div class="triggers-row" style="display: flex; gap: 8px; margin-top: 16px;">
						<img src="https://tryholo.ai/rootPage/assets/brandDna/triggerGreen.avif" alt="Disparador Verde" style="height: 32px; width: auto;" decoding="async" loading="lazy"/>
						<img src="https://tryholo.ai/rootPage/assets/brandDna/triggerYellow.avif" alt="Disparador Amarillo" style="height: 32px; width: auto;" decoding="async" loading="lazy"/>
						<img src="https://tryholo.ai/rootPage/assets/brandDna/triggerRed.avif" alt="Disparador Rojo" style="height: 32px; width: auto;" decoding="async" loading="lazy"/>
					</div>
				</article>

